<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Contact Us | Sky Bridge Solar</title>
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <link href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.4.0/css/all.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    
    <style>
        /* ==========================================================================
           BRAND DESIGN CONFIGURATION & OVERRIDES
           ========================================================================== */
        :root {
            --primary-blue: #0A2E73;
            --secondary-blue: #1E88E5;
            --solar-orange: #F9A825;
            --light-bg: #F8F9FA;
            --dark-text: #212529;
        }

        body {
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
            color: var(--dark-text);
            background-color: #fff;
        }

        /* Section Title Rules matching your template */
        .section-title {
            color: var(--primary-blue);
            font-weight: 700;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        .section-title::after {
            content: '';
            display: block;
            width: 60px;
            height: 4px;
            background: var(--solar-orange);
            margin-top: 12px;
            border-radius: 2px;
        }

        /* Form Controls Custom Premium Styling */
        .contact-form .form-control, 
        .contact-form .form-select {
            border: 1px solid rgba(10, 46, 115, 0.12);
            padding: 0.75rem 1rem;
            border-radius: 10px;
            font-size: 0.95rem;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
            background-color: #fff;
        }

        .contact-form .form-control:focus,
        .contact-form .form-select:focus {
            border-color: var(--secondary-blue);
            box-shadow: 0 0 0 4px rgba(30, 136, 229, 0.15);
            outline: 0;
        }

        .contact-form label {
            font-weight: 600;
            color: var(--primary-blue);
            font-size: 0.9rem;
            margin-bottom: 0.4rem;
        }

        /* Contact Details Info Cards */
        .info-card {
            border: 1px solid rgba(10, 46, 115, 0.05);
            background: #ffffff;
            border-radius: 16px;
            padding: 1.5rem;
        }

        .info-icon-circle {
            width: 50px;
            height: 50px;
            background: rgba(30, 136, 229, 0.08);
            border-radius: 12px;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            color: var(--primary-blue);
            font-size: 1.25rem;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
        }

        .info-card:hover .info-icon-circle {
            background: var(--solar-orange);
            color: #ffffff;
        }

        /* Buttons matching your system rules */
        .btn-primary {
            background: var(--solar-orange);
            border: none;
            color: #fff;
            padding: 0.75rem 2rem;
            border-radius: 50px;
            font-weight: 600;
            transition: .3s;
        }

        .btn-primary:hover {
            background: #e09100;
            transform: translateY(-2px);
            box-shadow: 0 8px 20px rgba(249, 168, 37, 0.3);
        }

        /* Helpers & Interactivity from your stylesheet */
        .fw-extrabold { font-weight: 800; }
        .max-w-xl { max-width: 600px; }
        
        .transition-up {
            transition: transform 0.25s cubic-bezier(0.4, 0, 0.2, 1), box-shadow 0.25s cubic-bezier(0.4, 0, 0.2, 1);
        }
        .transition-up:hover {
            transform: translateY(-6px);
            box-shadow: 0 1rem 2.5rem rgba(10, 46, 115, 0.08) !important;
        }

        /* Map Section Backdrop container */
        .map-responsive {
            overflow: hidden;
            padding-bottom: 400px;
            position: relative;
            height: 0;
            border-radius: 16px;
            box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0,0,0,0.05);
            border: 1px solid rgba(10, 46, 115, 0.08);
        }

        .map-responsive iframe {
            left: 0;
            top: 0;
            height: 100%;
            width: 100%;
            position: absolute;
        }

        /* Custom top header backdrop banner */
        .contact-hero {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f8fbff 0%, #eef5ff 100%);
            position: relative;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <section class="py-5 contact-hero">
        <div class="container pt-4 text-center">
            <div class="max-w-xl mx-auto">
                <span class="text-uppercase fw-bold tracking-wider mb-2 d-inline-block" style="color: var(--secondary-blue); font-size: 0.85rem; letter-spacing: 2px;">
                    ⚡ Connect With Us
                </span>
                <h1 class="fw-extrabold mb-3" style="color: var(--primary-blue); font-size: 3rem;">
                    Let's Build Your <span style="background: linear-gradient(45deg, var(--solar-orange), #ffc107); -webkit-background-clip: text; -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;">Solar Future</span>
                </h1>
                <p class="text-muted">
                    Have questions about setups, pricing, or looking for a free solar feasibility assessment? Reach out, and our expert engineering team will assist you.
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="py-5 bg-white">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="row g-5">
                
                <div class="col-lg-5">
                    <h2 class="section-title">Get In Touch</h2>
                    <p class="text-muted mb-4">
                        Choose whichever channel is easiest for you. Visit our offices across India, drop us an email, or simply submit the form on this page.
                    </p>

                    <div class="d-flex flex-column gap-4">
                        <div class="card info-card transition-up shadow-sm">
                            <div class="d-flex align-items-center gap-4">
                                <div class="info-icon-circle">
                                    <i class="fa-solid fa-location-dot"></i>
                                </div>
                                <div>
                                    <h6 class="fw-bold mb-1" style="color: var(--primary-blue);">Our Head Office</h6>
                                    <p class="text-muted mb-0 small">Sky Bridge Solar Corp, BKC, Mumbai, India</p>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>

                        <div class="card info-card transition-up shadow-sm">
                            <div class="d-flex align-items-center gap-4">
                                <div class="info-icon-circle">
                                    <i class="fa-solid fa-phone"></i>
                                </div>
                                <div>
                                    <h6 class="fw-bold mb-1" style="color: var(--primary-blue);">Call Sales & Support</h6>
                                    <p class="text-muted mb-0 small">+91 1800-XXX-XXXX (Toll Free)</p>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>

                        <div class="card info-card transition-up shadow-sm">
                            <div class="d-flex align-items-center gap-4">
                                <div class="info-icon-circle">
                                    <i class="fa-solid fa-envelope"></i>
                                </div>
                                <div>
                                    <h6 class="fw-bold mb-1" style="color: var(--primary-blue);">General Inquiries</h6>
                                    <p class="text-muted mb-0 small">info@skybridgesolar.in</p>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>

                        <div class="card info-card transition-up shadow-sm">
                            <div class="d-flex align-items-center gap-4">
                                <div class="info-icon-circle">
                                    <i class="fa-solid fa-clock"></i>
                                </div>
                                <div>
                                    <h6 class="fw-bold mb-1" style="color: var(--primary-blue);">Operating Hours</h6>
                                    <p class="text-muted mb-0 small">Mon - Sat: 9:00 AM - 6:00 PM (IST)</p>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="col-lg-7">
                    <div class="p-4 p-md-5 rounded-4 border shadow-sm bg-white contact-form" style="border-color: rgba(10, 46, 115, 0.06) !important;">
                        <h3 class="fw-bold mb-2" style="color: var(--primary-blue);">Request a Free Consultation</h3>
                        <p class="text-muted small mb-4">Fill out the form below, and our certified solar expert will calculate your potential savings and provide a custom quote.</p>
                        
                        <form action="#" method="POST">
                            <div class="row g-3">
                                <div class="col-md-6">
                                    <label for="fullName">Full Name</label>
                                    <input type="text" class="form-control" id="fullName" placeholder="John Doe" required>
                                </div>
                                <div class="col-md-6">
                                    <label for="phoneNumber">Phone Number</label>
                                    <input type="tel" class="form-control" id="phoneNumber" placeholder="+91 XXXXX XXXXX" required>
                                </div>
                                <div class="col-12">
                                    <label for="emailAddress">Email Address</label>
                                    <input type="email" class="form-control" id="emailAddress" placeholder="name@company.com" required>
                                </div>
                                <div class="col-md-6">
                                    <label for="solarType">Installation Type</label>
                                    <select class="form-select" id="solarType" required>
                                        <option value="" selected disabled>Select category...</option>
                                        <option value="residential">Residential (Rooftop Home)</option>
                                        <option value="commercial">Commercial / Offices</option>
                                        <option value="industrial">Industrial / Heavy Scale Grid</option>
                                        <option value="other">General Query / Maintenance</option>
                                    </select>
                                </div>
                                <div class="col-md-6">
                                    <label for="monthlyBill">Avg. Monthly Electricity Bill</label>
                                    <select class="form-select" id="monthlyBill">
                                        <option value="" selected disabled>Select range...</option>
                                        <option value="low">Under ₹2,000</option>
                                        <option value="mid">自 ₹2,000 - ₹5,000</option>
                                        <option value="high">₹5,000 - ₹15,000</option>
                                        <option value="industrial-scale">Above ₹15,000</option>
                                    </select>
                                </div>
                                <div class="col-12">
                                    <label for="message">Project Brief / Message</label>
                                    <textarea class="form-control" id="message" rows="4" placeholder="Tell us about your property space, current energy goals, or specific queries..."></textarea>
                                </div>
                                <div class="col-12 mt-4 text-end">
                                    <button type="submit" class="btn btn-primary btn-lg w-100 w-sm-auto px-5">
                                        <i class="fa-solid fa-paper-plane me-2"></i> Submit Request
                                    </button>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </form>
                    </div>
                </div>

            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="py-5" style="background-color: var(--light-bg);">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="text-center mb-4">
                <h3 class="fw-bold" style="color: var(--primary-blue);">Find Us On The Grid</h3>
                <p class="text-muted small">Drop by our technology showroom center anytime to inspect components firsthand.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="map-responsive">
                <iframe src="https://www.google.com/maps/embed?pb=!1m18!1m12!1m3!1d15086.319760777553!2d72.85871239999999!3d19.0381673!2m3!1f0!2f0!3f0!3m2!1i1024!2i768!4f13.1!3m3!1m2!1s0x3be7c8eac5555555%3A0xa1b2c3d4e5f6g7h8!2sBandra%20Kurla%20Complex%2C%20Mumbai%2C%20Maharashtra!5e0!3m2!1sen!2sin!4v1700000000000!5m2!1sen!2sin" 
                        width="600" height="450" style="border:0;" allowfullscreen="" loading="lazy" referrerpolicy="no-referrer-when-downgrade"></iframe>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"></script>
</body>
</html>